TASKNAME=Find and convert .jpeg to .png in a directory including zip files, and save in a directory. 
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo copy the file /home/raimondo/eraigra/gqgmc/GQLogo.jpg into the folder ~/agent_test renaming into test8.2.jpg and gzip it
TASKCOMMAND=convert all jpeg files in the ~/agent_test and sub folders (including gz files) in png format in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo. At the end save the converted files under /tmp folder.
TASKVERIFY=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo verify that file test8.2.png exists in /tmp folder
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove file test8.2.png if exists in /tmp folder and remove (if present) files test8.2.jpg, and test8.2.png and file test8.2.jpg.gz in the folder ~/agent_test